Package: micstoich
Title: Microbial Stoichiometry Calculations
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Sasha", "Hafner", email = "sasha.hafner@bce.au.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates stoichiometry of microbial reactions using the
    half-reaction approach from Rittmann and McCarty (2001). Supports aerobic
    respiration, anaerobic respiration, and fermentation with user-specified
    electron donor, acceptor, and synthesis fraction.
URL: https://github.com/AU-BCE-EE/micstoich
BugReports: https://github.com/AU-BCE-EE/micstoich/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
